name: Die For You
description:
A4
4961 x 7016

Someone who has never felt loved in his life. He is willing to do anything so that there is someone who appreciates and loves him sincerely. He has loved someone for a long time, but that someone doesn't love him. He will not give up until the end of his life, to win that someone's heart. Because, he believes this person can accompany, support, and change it for the better.
